<p>Agay itselfe is a small town you get to it via St. Raphael which is the bigger town in the area.
Agay seems to be comprised of mostly touristic buildings with no <em>normal</em> businesses.
We stayed at a big resort near Agay which consists of tourist bunkers :smile:, pools, restaurants and sport areas.</p>

