<p>Awesome food we ate at <em>Chez Georges</em> <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/g9im22LnCAkiCV8j6">google maps</a> - <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g1080032-d1333299-Reviews-Scarparo_le_Bluegreen-Agay_Saint_Raphael_French_Riviera_Cote_d_Azur_Provence_Alp.html?m=19905">tripadvisor</a>. He really is an artist.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Trip to Saint-Tropez</p>
</blockquote>

<p>We decided to also visit Saint Tropez.
Initially we wanted to go there by ferry but we screwed up translating the website and had to return from the harbor and go by car.
Actually, the traffic from Agay to Staint Tropez is insane :smile:.</p>

<p>When we arrived, we visited the harbor and looked at some expensive yachts, expensively clothed people and the the castle.
